          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When the guest issues RDPMC instructions, a VM exit occurs. When set, this flag instructs the kernel to handle RDRPMC VM exits directly, and more efficiently, than passing them on to user space.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
